<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234268>
    dc:description "FIGURES 38 – 45. Pompilinae spp., ♀, claw of hind leg. 38. Gonaporus alfierii. 39. G. ecbatanus. 40. G. e m i r a t u s sp. nov. 41. Eidopompilus arnoldi. 42. Microphadnus griseus. 43. Stigmaporus lystracantha. 44. S. wolfi. 45. Xenaporus (Baguenaia) vegteri. Scale bar 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234268/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234265>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 16. Habitus (dorsal view). 11, 12. Gonaporus israelicus. 13. Eidopompilus arnoldi. 14. Microphadnus griseus. 15. Xenaporus eremocanus. 16. Xenaporus (Baguenaia) vegteri. 11, 13 – 16, ♀; 12, ♂. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234265/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234269>
    dc:description "FIGURES 53 – 60. 53, 54. Stigmaporus wolfi, fore wing, ♀ (53) and ♂ (54). 55 – 60. Xenaporus spp., ♂, fore wing (55 – 57) and genitalia (58 – 60) (a, dorsal; b, ventral view). 55, 58. X. eremocanus. 56, 59. X. freidbergi. 57, 60. X. tamerlan." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234269/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234271>
    dc:description "FIGURES 66 – 71. Xenaporus ignoteremus, ♀. 66. Head (a, anterior; b, lateral; c, dorsal view). 67. Antenna. 68. Fore wing. 69. Hind wing. 70. Protarsus. 71. Metatarsus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234271/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234267>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29 – 37. Gonaporus and Xenaporus spp. (29, 30, 32 – 37, ♀; 31, ♂), metapostnotum (dorsal view). 29. G. alfierii. 30 – 32. G. israelicus from Israel (30, 31) and Mauritania (32). 33. G. ecbatanus. 34. G. simulator sp. nov. 35. G. spinosissimus sp. nov. 36. X. eremocanus. 37. X. tamerlan. Scale bar 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234267/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234280>
    dc:description "FIGURES 110 – 120. Gonaporus spp., ♀, antenna. 110. G. alfierii. 111. G. ecbatanus. 112. G. emiratus sp. nov. 113. G. gracilis. 114. G. israelicus. 115. G. maureanus. 116. G. mirabilis sp. nov. 117. G. omanicus. 118. G. setitarsus sp. nov. 119. G. simulator sp. nov. 120. G. spinosissimus sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234280/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234266>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 28. 17. Stigmaporus lystracantha, wing venation. 18, 19. Gonaporus spinosissimus sp. nov., metafemur (dorsal view of apical part). 20. Micraporus priesneri, wing venation. 21 – 23. Protarsus, dorsal view. 21. G. alfierii. 22. G. ecbatanus. 23. G. israelicus. 24 – 28. Protarsus, ventral view. 24. G. alfierii. 25. G. ecbatanus. 26. G. israelicus. 27. G. simulator sp. nov. 28. G. spinosissimus sp. nov. 17, 18, 20, 24 – 28, ♀; 19, 21 – 23, ♂. Scale bar 1 mm for 17 and 0.5 mm for 18 – 28." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234266/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234282>
    dc:description "FIGURES 131 – 141. Gonaporus spp., ♀, protarsus (posterior spines of tarsal comb are not shadowed; anteroventral spines are shadowed). 131. G. alfierii. 132. G. ecbatanus. 133. G. emiratus sp. nov. 134. G. gracilis. 135. G. israelicus. 136. G. maureanus. 137. G. mirabilis sp. nov. 138. G. omanicus. 139. G. setitarsus sp. nov. 140. G. simulator sp. nov. 141. G. spinosissimus sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234282/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234281>
    dc:description "FIGURES 121 – 130. Gonaporus spp., ♂, antenna. 121. G. alfierii. 122. G. ecbatanus. 123. G. emiratus sp. nov. 124. G. gracilis. 125. G. israelicus. 126. G. jaziratensis sp. nov. 127. G. mirabilis sp. nov. 128. G. setitarsus sp. nov. 129. G. simulator sp. nov. 130. G. spinosissimus sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234281/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234290>
    dc:description "FIGURES 200 – 207. Gonaporus and Xenaporus spp., ♂, subgenital plate (a, ventral; b, lateral; c, dorsal view). 200. G. alfierii. 201. G. ecbatanus. 202. G. emiratus sp. nov. 203. G. gracilis. 204. G. israelicus. 205. G. jaziratensis sp. nov. 206. G. setitarsus sp. nov. 207. X. ignoteremus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234290/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

